contentrichtext.text: '''James Reilly''' is the name of: *[[James Bernard Reilly]] (1845–1924), U.S. Representative from Pennsylvania *[[James E. Reilly]] (1948–2008), American television script writer *[[James F. Reilly]] (born 1954), American astronaut *[[James D. J. Reilly]] (born 1760), famous rebel in several rebellions, including the American and French revolutions *[[James W. Reilly]] (1828–1905), American Civil War general in the Union Army and Ohio state representative *[[James Reilly (Canadian politician)]] (c. 1830–1909), Canadian businessman and Mayor of Calgary *[[James Reilly (Irish politician)]] (born 1955), Irish Fine Gael politician *[[Jim Reilly]] (born 1957), drummer for punk band Stiff Little Fingers ==See also== *[[James Riley (disambiguation)]] *[[James O'Reilly (disambiguation)]] {{hndis|name = Reilly, James}}
